41:16.352 --> 41:18.096
- I was looking for.
- <i>I can't believe she knows.</i>

41:18.120 --> 41:20.189
<i>She's dragging me
on a trip with Anna. I...</i>

41:20.623 --> 41:23.225
- What is this? Wh... what is this?
- <i>God, I fucked this up.</i>

41:23.392 --> 41:25.928
<i>- It's gonna be okay.
- I'm telling you,</i>

41:26.262 --> 41:27.429
she is vicious.

41:28.864 --> 41:31.500
You have no idea.

41:31.734 --> 41:33.269
I have to be
more careful from now on.

41:33.502 --> 41:36.872
Everything will be different
when I get back, Vivienne.

41:37.039 --> 41:38.974
I will file the divorce papers,

41:39.041 --> 41:40.876
and we can start
our new life together.

41:41.010 --> 41:44.146
- No, no, no, no!
- Yes, yes.

41:44.413 --> 41:45.414
- No.
- Yes.

41:45.481 --> 41:47.049
- Come on.
- It's okay.

41:48.684 --> 41:50.819
Jessica, please.

41:50.886 --> 41:53.956
- I don't know what's going on right now.
- <i>I love you so much.</i>

41:54.723 --> 41:56.125
