That was real. That was real.

42:17.946 --> 42:20.149
So, you've been seeing Vivienne.

42:20.849 --> 42:23.185
Yeah? Yeah?

42:23.886 --> 42:26.422
And you... you...
You're going to... to...

42:27.389 --> 42:29.024
You're going to divorce me?

42:30.559 --> 42:31.593
I... no.

42:31.994 --> 42:34.129
I said that to her,
but I didn't mean it.

42:35.664 --> 42:36.899
My god.

42:36.965 --> 42:39.134
