both of us this entire time

42:39.201 --> 42:40.636
and you've been lying to me.

42:41.003 --> 42:42.404
I can't believe this.

42:42.638 --> 42:44.673
No, hey, listen,
don't get emotional.

42:44.873 --> 42:46.375
I can get however I want.

42:46.508 --> 42:50.279
- Not in front of Anna.
- Not in front of Anna? You're a piece of shit.

42:51.914 --> 42:53.549
Dad, are you leaving me and mom?

43:01.890 --> 43:03.926
I'm gonna kill you.

43:05.060 --> 43:06.060
Look.

43:06.295 --> 43:09.164
<i>Greatest hits</i>
<i>of gene Allison.</i> See?

43:10.199 --> 43:13.902
No. You're a liar
and so is that boy.

43:14.403 --> 43:16.672
You're doing this
to mess with me.

43:17.072 --> 43:18.512
Anna and I are gonna
leave right now.

43:18.574 --> 43:19.951
- Please don't.
- You... you're disgusting.

43:19.975 --> 43:21.543
- Please don't.
- You see this?

43:22.444 --> 43:23.444
Go to hell.

43:23.946 --> 43:25.481
Yeah, I'm divorcing you now.

43:25.547 --> 43:26.315
We're done.

43:26.382 --> 43:27.516
- Listen to me...
- I'm out.

43:27.583 --> 43:28.583
Jessica!

43:28.852 --> 43:31.029
- Come on. I want you to get up. Get up.
- No, you can't leave dad.

43:31.053 --> 43:33.122
- Jessica!
- I'm out.

43:34.523 --> 43:37.326
Hey, guys. What'd I miss?

43:38.227 --> 43:39.261
Toby?

43:43.732 --> 43:46.635
Oh, my god.

43:47.804 --> 43:50.406
Wait. I figured it out.

43:59.515 --> 44:01.016
Other than Anna...

44:02.317 --> 44:04.319
You're all in on this,
aren't you?

44:07.656 --> 44:09.725
- In on what?
- In on this.

44:10.559 --> 44:12.694
You're all working together,
aren't you?

44:14.763 --> 44:15.763
You and the old man,

44:15.799 --> 44:18.367
both have keys
to the locked room.

44:18.934 --> 44:19.934
And you,

44:20.569 --> 44:23.105
you already know these people
and you paid them.

44:23.272 --> 44:26.141
You set me up
and taped me somehow

44:26.241 --> 44:28.177
and now, you're getting
your sick revenge.

44:28.243 --> 44:30.345
You don't want
to rebuild our marriage.

44:30.412 --> 44:31.480
You want revenge.

44:31.613 --> 44:34.249
- You're crazy.
- You know, I knew you were vicious

44:34.316 --> 44:35.350
I knew it,

44:35.451 --> 44:37.686
but I didn't know
you were a psychopath.

44:38.587 --> 44:40.322
How could you do this to Anna?

44:40.422 --> 44:42.591
I've never met
these people before in my life.

44:43.292 --> 44:44.492
I'm calling the police on you.

44:44.593 --> 44:45.970
